# Tauri signing keys — must NEVER be committed. The literal `~/` folder
# below is a Windows artifact: `npx tauri signer generate -w ~/.tauri/...`
# doesn't expand `~` on Windows and creates the dir relative to the repo.
~/
*.key
*.key.pub
